ps://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[2253,3453,10987,63903,168775],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"论文链接：https://arxiv.org/abs/2503.16954 重子 CP 破坏最终被中国 LHCb 合作组发现了！首次在 B 重子衰变过程中观测到 CP 破坏现象，该现象非常重要，与物理学中哪些问题有关联，与你的研究有何联系？"},"attached_info":"CkoIiam11cHEwNBQEAMaCTExNDE0MzE2OCCcq4O/BjAAOJABQBFyEzE4ODc0NzAzMzk1OTgwMzQzOTh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"80 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-c94d729187e933833ff743d2f700dd01_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"18_1743042543.307305","card_id":"Q_665731716","card_label":{"type":"new","icon":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png","night_icon":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"},"target":{"id":665731716,"title":"为什么transformer的FFN需要先升维再降维？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/665731716","type":"question","created":1725016761,"answer_count":15,"follower_count":227,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[3279,372847,401598,3024391],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"W_2矩阵一般是4d\\times d的，那么它的rank最高为d，也就是说至少有3d行可以被其他行线性表出，假设某个inputx\\in R^{1\\times d}在经过W_1以及激活函数后的hidden state为h\\in R^{1\\times 4d}那么FFN的outputh\\cdot W_2可以看作是对W_2的4d行进行一个加权求和\\sum_{i=1}^{4d}{h_i}W_{2,i}，其中h_i代表h的第i个分量，W_{2,i}代表W_2的第i行。由于W_2的低秩特性，我总可以在W_2找到n(n\\leq d)个线性无关的行(假设就是前n行)，从而对于任意1\\leq i\\leq 4d，W_{2,i}都可以由这n行线性表出W_{2,i}=\\sum_{j=1}^{n}{c_j}W_{2,j}，所以上述加权求和总可以进行改写：\\sum_{i=1}^{4d}{h_i}W_{2,i}=\\sum_{i=1}^{n}{k_i}W_{2,i}，那么W_2矩阵只需要这n行即可，模型只需要学习到如何通过W_1和激活函数来得到“新的”h'\\in R^{1\\times n}=\\{k_1, k_2,...,k_n\\}，那么这么看完全不需要现在的FFN中先升维再降维的操作，所以为什么降低FFN中矩阵的维度实践中往往效果会变差呢？"},"attached_info":"CkAIiam11cHEwNBQEAMaCTExMDIxNzk0OCC51ca2BjAAOOMBQBJyCTY2NTczMTcxNngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_